Thanks to Saman [ https://substack.com/redirect/46471763-3266-403f-af85-7e3=
85b8d0017?r=3D9p0gt ] for working with me on the piece, Garry [ https://sub=
stack.com/redirect/f98093bf-0851-4b3c-bf38-41df45817385?r=3D9p0gt ] for the=
 intro, and Dan [ https://substack.com/redirect/f9bc854c-3446-4f5f-abb6-05f=
fb4d6c15a?r=3D9p0gt ] for editing!=20
That=E2=80=99s all for today. See you back here Friday for your Weekly Dose=
 of Optimism. Have a great week.
Thanks for reading,
Packy

